            <h3 data-uuid="f79747e304b542158612a8d7a054f58b">Part 2: Write an
                Explanatory Essay</h3>
            <h6 data-uuid="d50409a7590e4fe9af5577812a2ef01a">Historical Context</h6>
            <p data-uuid="19d97b6375bd49768dc0f1d5cac94827">The nation heaved a collective sigh of relief with news of the armistice
                that brought peace at the end of “the war to end all wars” in 1918. Americans
                looked forward to peace and prosperity, and the country embarked on a frenzied
                era of progress, plenty, and social change known as the Roaring Twenties. </p>
            <h6 data-uuid="ca97c8b5962d47719ca14e99b7be4ee5">Task</h6>
            <p data-uuid="71fa1ad2925144d9b2a2f90d23af0410">The 1920s heralded a period of unprecedented and swift social
                change in American society. It also was a period of economic prosperity. Write
                an essay in which you explain what factors contributed to the social and
                cultural changes that altered the American way of life in the Roaring Twenties.
            </p>
            <p data-uuid="2006ea55ba3c44c7b576d17135df08fd">Complete the following steps as you plan and compose your essay.</p>
            <ol data-uuid="d6c9e8ce8dec4ba381ae2b1404576003">
                <li data-uuid="7e7cd76e27e348f59ce8acdd8315086b">Review your notes and sources before you
                    start writing.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="d0eefce195a14bb28e90fc719b844dce">Use at least <i>two</i> of the sources in Part 1,
                    and develop the topic with relevant, well-chosen text or visual evidence from
                    the documents.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="f4471d9dc62b4f33be604d8ce8aeb072">Cite specific text or visual evidence from
                    each of the sources in your response.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="747f283183964149a35153546540e6fb">Plan your essay so that it includes an
                    introduction, several body paragraphs, and a concluding paragraph.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="4025a1aba1c84683b9fd0b2b221c9ef5">Organize your essay in a clear and logical
                    way that focuses on the topic and supports it with explanations and facts.</li>
                <li data-uuid="cffdac34a15e4f788e1354dbb35986ad">Write a conclusion that sums up your ideas and
                    supports the information you present.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>
